{"tid":946300,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個你愛但會傷害你既人，一個你唔愛但唔會傷害你既人","createTime":"2018-12-18T12:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T04:01:41.000Z","uid":38954,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f85794bc57a3fa9ac9dd36930a15cbf976ad3113","tid":946300,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"兩者對你既愛都一樣<br />\n你會點揀？"},{"pid":"aeabe7d77d1ea1c9eb8142f081533a381fbeb837","tid":946300,"uid":215059,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"我會揀後者<br />\n揀前者終有一日你會因為佢傷害你而慢慢失去當中嘅感情<br />\n揀後者至少知道佢唔會傷害你，唔使日日擔心<br />\n珍惜一個會一直對你好嘅人<br />\n知道佢終有一日會傷害你，一齊得嘅開心只會係短暫，更會令你日日夜夜擔心大家嘅關係<br />\n雖則好多人，尤其女仔會揀前者<br />\n有得揀當然想揀既係你鍾意又唔會傷害你嘅人<br />\n但係又幾難遇到呢"},{"pid":"ff3025e0b76e8f9d206a2fab4a6cd236c6882a10","tid":946300,"uid":204803,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"冇得揀，因為唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038db65a29892b5850d0534637bcb5e56303f184","tid":946300,"uid":78683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"講到好似我有得揀咁"},{"pid":"dc48e05a91d4c8e9a7f8e154a036347e8061b1ea","tid":946300,"uid":215059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"038db65a29892b5850d0534637bcb5e56303f184","tid":946300,"uid":78683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"講到好似我有得揀咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"就係冇得我去揀<br />\n所以就係想其他人揀個真心為自己好嘅人"},{"pid":"1c58620a80f588d9cfb1a92857a04cf86dd70bb4","tid":946300,"uid":205656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"你有得揀咩。你冇啊"},{"pid":"9ede2d74bbf7ccb787546846157b2c369bec6276","tid":946300,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"前者叫過雞背叛過我<br />\n如果佢肯改 係咪同自己愛既人一齊會幸福啲？"},{"pid":"6efff82a664986701a20ed5367908224b9c2b51